<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب س م ل:</span> <span class="c2">(بَسْمَلَ)</span> الرَّجُلُ إِذَا قَالَ بِسْمِ اللَّهِ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> قَدْ أَكْثَرْتَ مِنَ الْبَسْمَلَةِ أَيْ مِنْ قَوْلِ بِسْمِ اللَّهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>